  "texts": [
    " As the rule-based component becomes more sophisticated to cover various linguistic nuances, the complexity increases, making it harder to maintain the system.",
    " Designing an effective model requires expertise in both machine learning and deep learning, and good knowledge to combine the different components.",
    "Initially, NER algorithms are designed for English language, similar techniques can be adapted to work with Indian languages such as Hindi, Sanskrit, Punjabi, Sindhi, Urdu, Malayalam and Marathi etc.",
    "Here, are some algorithms to implement for NER using Indian languages.",
    "(a) Hidden Markov ModelIt is a statistical model that assumes there is an underlying hidden sequence of states that generates observable symbols."
  ]
}